General Information of this Script

                                    ## **Aim of the Script** 

##### To define all the chromatin states based on the marks from the 4 histone marks used in this study.
##### To generate all the peaks files for Transcriptional factors in Neighborhood ZONE(TFinZONE) in all of teh stages as reference (01dcpi, 04dcpi and 14dcpi)

## **Input files**
   ##### COMBI_META_ALL_COMBINA.csv
      - Quantification from the enrichment of all histone marks used in this study.
   ##### META_ZF_heart_re_HISTONTES.txt 
      - Metadata from all histone marks used in this study.
    
   ##### 001ZF_Geno_Areas_bedto_HEATMAP_MAT_ALL.txt
      - All the H3K4me3 peaks summarised in this manuscript
   ##### ENH_BIVA_EM_REF_NON_OVER_ENH_ALL_for_forUCSC.bed
      - All H3K4me3 peaks annotated.

   ##### MAT_all_HM_Zf_danRer11_BWAVE_A.txt
      - Quantification from the enrichment of all histone marks used in this study.

dir.create(PTHA_3_01)
MA49_01_9u1<- list()
for(i in 1:length(NAME_ENH$Var1)) {
#print(i)
 MA49_01_9u1[[i]]<- subset(MA49_01_9u,ENH4==NAME_ENH[i,1],select=c("V1","V2","V3","PEAK_ID2","ENH4"))
write.table(MA49_01_9u1[[i]],file=paste(PTHA_3_01,NAME_ENH[i,1],DCPI,"forMOTIF.bed",sep=""),sep="\t",row.names = F,col.names=F,dec=".",quote = F)
}
